{"tid":2362461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反擊！Parler遭封殺 美眾議員要求調查蘋果、谷歌、亞馬遜","createTime":"2021-01-11T12:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T19:32:32.000Z","uid":57073,"like":187,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"679007888ff103986c59c862fc63502c6e0e2d15","tid":2362461,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:44:59.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕在美國國會暴動後，蘋果、谷歌、亞馬遜聯手封殺川粉平台Parler，對此共和黨眾議員努尼斯（Devin Nunes）展開反擊，要求對這3家巨頭展開詐欺調查。<br />\n<br />\n據《福斯新聞》報導，努尼斯表示，蘋果、谷歌、亞馬遜的行為，已經觸犯了反壟斷法（又稱反托拉斯法），也違反了公民權利和詐騙及貪汙集團犯罪法（Racketeer Influenced and Corrupt Organizations）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3407486\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3407486&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BcIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=1418b2e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3407486&h=a8615feb\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3407486</a>"},{"pid":"2c3eef32fedd7ff46744132d956e2e7ae2c390aa","tid":2362461,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:50:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e12060e836f2346eac489f14c3bc63055c6a7114","tid":2362461,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:51:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aeaa0accb5fc238bfd2ea0ece2bb5e23a6a9b40","tid":2362461,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass